{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-11",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_11_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Fat Man",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 5,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 967.02,
  "page_end_sec": 1208.88,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.574,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 967.02,
      "end": 969.14,
      "text": "Then Spade rose and stood close to the fat man,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 969.22,
      "end": 970.1,
      "text": "looking down at him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 970.58,
      "end": 971.82,
      "text": "and Spade's eyes were hard"
    },
    {
      "start": 971.82,
      "end": 972.22,
      "text": "and bright."
    },
    {
      "start": 972.48,
      "end": 974.04,
      "text": "He raised his glass."
    },
    {
      "start": 974.28,
      "end": 975.74,
      "text": "His voice was deliberate,"
    },
    {
      "start": 975.94,
      "end": 976.46,
      "text": "challenging:"
    },
    {
      "start": 977.696,
      "end": 978.52,
      "text": "\"Here's to plain speaking"
    },
    {
      "start": 978.74,
      "end": 979.54,
      "text": "and clear understanding.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 980.51,
      "end": 982.4,
      "text": "The fat man chuckled and they drank.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 982.73,
      "end": 984.22,
      "text": "The fat man sat down."
    },
    {
      "start": 984.86,
      "end": 985.64,
      "text": "He held his glass"
    },
    {
      "start": 985.8,
      "end": 988.62,
      "text": "against his belly with both hands and smiled up at Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 989.28,
      "end": 989.64,
      "text": "He said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 989.82,
      "end": 990.54,
      "text": "\"Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 990.54,
      "end": 990.78,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 990.92,
      "end": 991.72,
      "text": "it's surprising,"
    },
    {
      "start": 992.38,
      "end": 995.28,
      "text": "but it well may be a fact that neither of"
    },
    {
      "start": 995.28,
      "end": 997.54,
      "text": "them does know exactly what that bird is"
    },
    {
      "start": 997.78,
      "end": 1002.68,
      "text": "and that nobody in all this whole wide sweet world knows what it is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1002.78,
      "end": 1003.92,
      "text": "saving and excepting"
    },
    {
      "start": 1004.22,
      "end": 1005.44,
      "text": "only your humble servant,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1005.64,
      "end": 1006.76,
      "text": "Casper Gutman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1006.9,
      "end": 1007.52,
      "text": "Esquire.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1008.33,
      "end": 1009.08,
      "text": "\"Swell.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1009.22,
      "end": 1010.98,
      "text": "Spade stood with legs apart,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1011.28,
      "end": 1012.24,
      "text": "one hand in"
    },
    {
      "start": 1012.24,
      "end": 1013.08,
      "text": "his trousers-pocket,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1013.58,
      "end": 1014.64,
      "text": "the other holding his glass."
    },
    {
      "start": 1015.19,
      "end": 1016.34,
      "text": "\"When you've told me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1016.46,
      "end": 1017.9,
      "text": "there'll only be two of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 1017.9,
      "end": 1018.26,
      "text": "who know.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1019.148,
      "end": 1020.508,
      "text": "\"Mathematically correct,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1020.508,
      "end": 1020.948,
      "text": "sir\"—"
    },
    {
      "start": 1020.948,
      "end": 1023.068,
      "text": "the fat man's eyes twinkled—"
    },
    {
      "start": 1023.068,
      "end": 1024.828,
      "text": "\"but\"—his smile spread—"
    },
    {
      "start": 1025.22,
      "end": 1025.62,
      "text": "I don't"
    },
    {
      "start": 1025.70,
      "end": 1026.688,
      "text": "know for certain"
    },
    {
      "start": 1026.688,
      "end": 1028.208,
      "text": "that I'm going to tell you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1029.6,
      "end": 1030.42,
      "text": "\"Don't be a damned fool,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1030.62,
      "end": 1031.5,
      "text": "Spade said patiently."
    },
    {
      "start": 1032.24,
      "end": 1032.74,
      "text": "You know what"
    },
    {
      "start": 1032.9,
      "end": 1033.1,
      "text": "it is."
    },
    {
      "start": 1033.88,
      "end": 1034.98,
      "text": "I know where it is."
    },
    {
      "start": 1035.08,
      "end": 1036.18,
      "text": "That's why we're here.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1036.78,
      "end": 1037.38,
      "text": "\"Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1037.4,
      "end": 1037.64,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1037.82,
      "end": 1038.74,
      "text": "where is it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1039.584,
      "end": 1040.9,
      "text": "Spade ignored the question.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1041.8,
      "end": 1043.06,
      "text": "The fat man bunched his lips,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1043.16,
      "end": 1044.02,
      "text": "raised his eyebrows,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1044.16,
      "end": 1046.1,
      "text": "and cocked his head a little to the left."
    },
    {
      "start": 1046.62,
      "end": 1046.92,
      "text": "\"You see,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.02,
      "end": 1047.74,
      "text": "he said blandly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.94,
      "end": 1049.56,
      "text": "I must tell you what I know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1049.7,
      "end": 1051.78,
      "text": "but you will not tell me what you know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1052.42,
      "end": 1053.48,
      "text": "That is hardly equitable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1053.74,
      "end": 1054.0,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 1054.22,
      "end": 1054.94,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1055.02,
      "end": 1055.16,
      "text": "no,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1055.18,
      "end": 1057.42,
      "text": "I do not think we can do business along those lines.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1058.46,
      "end": 1060.1,
      "text": "Spade's face became pale and hard.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1060.46,
      "end": 1061.98,
      "text": "He spoke rapidly in a low"
    },
    {
      "start": 1062.04,
      "end": 1062.9,
      "text": "furious voice:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1063.68,
      "end": 1064.8,
      "text": "\"Think again and think fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 1065.5,
      "end": 1067.5,
      "text": "I told that punk of yours that you'd have"
    },
    {
      "start": 1067.5,
      "end": 1069.14,
      "text": "to talk to me before you got through."
    },
    {
      "start": 1069.92,
      "end": 1071.5,
      "text": "I'll tell you now that you'll do your"
    },
    {
      "start": 1071.5,
      "end": 1073.6,
      "text": "talking today or you are through."
    },
    {
      "start": 1074.56,
      "end": 1076.0,
      "text": "What are you wasting my time for?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1076.46,
      "end": 1077.64,
      "text": "You and your lousy secret!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1078.24,
      "end": 1078.7,
      "text": "Christ!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1079.64,
      "end": 1081.94,
      "text": "I know exactly what that stuff is that"
    },
    {
      "start": 1081.952,
      "end": 1083.79,
      "text": "they keep in the sub-treasury vaults."
    },
    {
      "start": 1084.42,
      "end": 1085.54,
      "text": "But what good does that do me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1085.96,
      "end": 1087.82,
      "text": "I can get along without you."
    },
    {
      "start": 1087.98,
      "end": 1088.92,
      "text": "God damn you!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1089.952,
      "end": 1091.98,
      "text": "Maybe you could have got along without me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1092.42,
      "end": 1093.58,
      "text": "if you'd kept clear of me."
    },
    {
      "start": 1093.72,
      "end": 1094.76,
      "text": "You can't now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1095.04,
      "end": 1096.24,
      "text": "Not in San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "start": 1097.16,
      "end": 1098.78,
      "text": "You'll come in or you'll get out—"
    },
    {
      "start": 1098.96,
      "end": 1099.98,
      "text": "and you'll do it today.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1101.1,
      "end": 1105.04,
      "text": "He turned and with angry heedlessness tossed his glass at the table.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1105.78,
      "end": 1106.8,
      "text": "The glass struck the wood,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1106.86,
      "end": 1108.84,
      "text": "burst apart, and splashed its contents"
    },
    {
      "start": 1109.36,
      "end": 1110.1,
      "text": "and glittering fragments"
    },
    {
      "start": 1110.6,
      "end": 1111.64,
      "text": "over table and floor."
    },
    {
      "start": 1112.0,
      "end": 1112.1,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1113.18,
      "end": 1114.74,
      "text": "deaf and blind to the crash,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1115.1,
      "end": 1116.86,
      "text": "wheeled to confront the fat man again."
    },
    {
      "start": 1117.96,
      "end": 1119.46,
      "text": "The fat man paid no more attention",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1119.46,
      "end": 1121.28,
      "text": "to the glass's fate than Spade did:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1122.112,
      "end": 1122.84,
      "text": "lips pursed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1122.86,
      "end": 1123.82,
      "text": "eyebrows raised,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1124.2,
      "end": 1125.94,
      "text": "head cocked a little to the left,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1126.04,
      "end": 1129.64,
      "text": "he had maintained his pink-faced blandness throughout Spade's"
    },
    {
      "start": 1129.7,
      "end": 1130.34,
      "text": "angry speech,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1130.98,
      "end": 1132.04,
      "text": "and he maintained it now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1132.32,
      "end": 1132.42,
      "text": "Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1133.36,
      "end": 1133.9,
      "text": "still furious,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1134.04,
      "end": 1134.34,
      "text": "said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1134.9,
      "end": 1136.44,
      "text": "\"And another thing, I don't want—\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1136.92,
      "end": 1139.02,
      "text": "The door to Spade's left opened.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1139.24,
      "end": 1141.5,
      "text": "The boy who had admitted Spade came in."
    },
    {
      "start": 1141.62,
      "end": 1142.98,
      "text": "He shut the door,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1143.14,
      "end": 1144.12,
      "text": "stood in front of it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1144.4,
      "end": 1146.4,
      "text": "with his hands flat against his flanks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1146.72,
      "end": 1147.52,
      "text": "and looked at Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1147.79,
      "end": 1148.9,
      "text": "The boy's eyes"
    },
    {
      "start": 1148.9,
      "end": 1151.18,
      "text": "were wide open and dark with wide pupils."
    },
    {
      "start": 1151.96,
      "end": 1154.38,
      "text": "Their gaze ran over Spade's body from shoulders to knees"
    },
    {
      "start": 1154.62,
      "end": 1157.12,
      "text": "and up again to settle on the handkerchief whose"
    },
    {
      "start": 1157.12,
      "end": 1159.12,
      "text": "maroon border peeped from the breast-pocket of"
    },
    {
      "start": 1159.2,
      "end": 1159.98,
      "text": "Spade's brown coat."
    },
    {
      "start": 1160.992,
      "end": 1161.44,
      "text": "\"Another thing,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1161.58,
      "end": 1162.18,
      "text": "Spade repeated,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1162.49,
      "end": 1163.52,
      "text": "glaring at the boy:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1164.32,
      "end": 1165.98,
      "text": "\"Keep that gunsel away from me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1166.4,
      "end": 1167.68,
      "text": "while you're making up your mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 1168.2,
      "end": 1168.76,
      "text": "I'll kill him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1168.82,
      "end": 1169.84,
      "text": "I don't like him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1169.98,
      "end": 1171.14,
      "text": "He makes me nervous."
    },
    {
      "start": 1171.4,
      "end": 1172.2,
      "text": "I'll kill"
    },
    {
      "start": 1172.3,
      "end": 1173.86,
      "text": "him the first time he gets in my way."
    },
    {
      "start": 1174.1,
      "end": 1176.28,
      "text": "I won't give him an even break."
    },
    {
      "start": 1176.5,
      "end": 1178.02,
      "text": "I won't give him a chance."
    },
    {
      "start": 1178.24,
      "end": 1178.94,
      "text": "I'll kill him.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1179.31,
      "end": 1181.96,
      "text": "The boy's lips twitched in a shadowy smile.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1182.28,
      "end": 1184.22,
      "text": "He neither raised his eyes nor spoke."
    },
    {
      "start": 1185.08,
      "end": 1186.23,
      "text": "The fat man said tolerantly:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1186.62,
      "end": 1186.752,
      "text": "\"Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1187.12,
      "end": 1187.32,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1187.48,
      "end": 1190.08,
      "text": "I must say you have a most violent temper.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1190.32,
      "end": 1191.36,
      "text": "\"Temper?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1191.58,
      "end": 1193.14,
      "text": "Spade laughed crazily."
    },
    {
      "start": 1193.6,
      "end": 1196.6,
      "text": "He crossed to the chair on which he had dropped his hat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1196.9,
      "end": 1198.76,
      "text": "picked up the hat, and set it on his head."
    },
    {
      "start": 1199.66,
      "end": 1202.4,
      "text": "He held out a long arm that ended in a thick"
    },
    {
      "start": 1202.4,
      "end": 1204.42,
      "text": "forefinger pointing at the fat man's belly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1205.16,
      "end": 1206.58,
      "text": "His angry voice filled the room."
    },
    {
      "start": 1207.38,
      "end": 1208.88,
      "text": "\"Think it over and think like hell."
    }
  ],
  "corrected": "claude"
}